<text top="105" left="55" width="499" height="15" font="font9" id="p1_t9" reading_order_no="6" segment_no="4" tag_type="title"><b>The integration of lipid-sensing and anti-inflammatory effects: how </b></text>
<text top="123" left="55" width="320" height="15" font="font9" id="p1_t10" reading_order_no="7" segment_no="4" tag_type="title"><b>the PPARs play a role in metabolic balance</b></text>
<text top="140" left="55" width="123" height="14" font="font10" id="p1_t11" reading_order_no="8" segment_no="5" tag_type="text">Alistair VW Nunn*</text>
<text top="140" left="178" width="6" height="10" font="font11" id="p1_t12" reading_order_no="9" segment_no="5" tag_type="text">1</text>
<text top="140" left="184" width="79" height="14" font="font10" id="p1_t13" reading_order_no="10" segment_no="5" tag_type="text">, Jimmy Bell</text>
